message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which is tailored to meet your specific needs. Given its value and the benefits it provides, I believe we can come to an agreement that is mutually beneficial. I am offering this exceptional product to you for $9,500. This price reflects the high quality and unique features of the product, while also considering your valuation of $10,000. I look forward to your response and the opportunity to discuss how this product can enhance your experience.
